2. Difficult to change phone numbers, told to go to the provider etc. Asked to wait for days. 
3. Strangely. Grab requires that if you change an account you must use a savings book. While Superbank doesn't have one, so you will always be a Superbank expert. 
4. Says it will be disbursed 2x a day, but not always 
5. Often holds merchant money, held back from being disbursed, this is the reason why it must be reported. But the bank report is not registered in the Grab report section. Strange.

If I had a lot of free time, I would also report to OJK, DPR, etc. The bank is disturbing and misleading. Going around and around for no reason. You're still lucky that I don't have time to take care of you. So it would be better to just fix the cooperation with Grab merchants. Don't make it difficult if you want to change to another account.

(Original)

Mereka melakukan promosi dengan iming2 dana akan cair 2x sehari. Secara otomatis namanya usaha apalagi resto ya tergiurlah untuk mengganti rekening penampungan. Yg sebelumnya saya pake BNI.

5. Sering nahan uang merchant ditahan ga cair alasannya inilah itulah harus report. Tapi report banknya ternyata gak terdaftar dibagian report grabnya. Aneh.

(Translated by Google) The CS really didn't provide any solutions, it felt like I was chatting with AI, what happened this morning when I tried to log in, I couldn't and ended up uninstalling and reinstalling it and then I could log in but didn't think about transferring money. Well, for a few hours I tried to log in to the app, but it couldn't work again and tried the same method but still couldn't, I tried looking for a solution to get it working, it turned out I had to switch from WiFi to a package and finally used an internet package but after that I was directed to the call center, where is the problem? How come when I called, I was directed to close my account?!!, so I ended the call, afraid that my account would really be closed unilaterally.

I panicked and tried to open Grab, but I was able to access some of my money and immediately transfer it to another bank. However, I couldn't access the money in another pocket. I tried various methods, but ended up being directed to the call center. I tried emailing, but there was no response. I tried DMing on Twitter and Instagram, but the template responses weren't helpful. I ended up having to give up some of my money, huhuhuhu.

Well, to everyone, be careful if there's any indication of an error, transfer the funds immediately. Don't let something like me happen and be helpless. I hope this bank doesn't cause too much harm to customers in the future, can improve its service system, and be more responsive. Thank you for your salary. ğŸ™ğŸ»

message:
(Translated by Google) The customer service is lacking. Initially, I reported it by calling and was directed to the live chat in the app. In live chat, the response was a bit slow, so I had to call customer care to request a faster response. The request was a bit unreasonable. I sent proof that there was no transaction, but it wasn't considered sufficient... What else could I do? Finally, I screen-recorded the transaction and sent it to the live chat.

The story didn't end there. I was asked to wait 7 business days. While waiting until the due date arrived, there was no response via email. I emailed first. And the response? Very unhelpful... The email response was the problem I reported (it said the transaction was successful. Oh, that's exactly it: it was successful but the money didn't arrive, that's the problem). I replied, and to date, there's been no further response.

I initially wanted to follow up via live chat, thinking it would be quicker than email. But for some reason, I can't open a new chat; there's no button or option. It ends at "Chat ended on..." and I can't restart it.

Oh, honestly, I'm so tired. My money is gone, it's been deducted but not received. Maybe we should just accept it...

Edit: The issue has been resolved, and the customer care department has called me to explain the details in detail. Thank you, and I hope we can continue to improve in the future.

(Original)
Customer servicenya kurang. Awalnya saya report by call, diarahkan live chat di aplikasi. Di live chat, responnya sedikit lama sampai saya harus call customer care untuk meminta responnya agak lebih cepat. Permintaannya agak ga masuk akal, sudah saya kirimkan bukti tidak ada transaksi, tapi tidak dianggap cukup.... Mau kaya gimana lagi? Sampai akhirnya saya screen record dan dikirimkan ke live chat itu.

Cerita tidak selesai di situ. Saya diminta tunggu 7 hari kerja. Selama menunggu hingga tibalah due date, tidak ada satupun email respon. Saya email duluan. Dan responnya? Sangat tidak membantu... Jawaban emailnya adalah masalah yang saya laporkan (katanya, transaksi sudah berhasil. loh ya justru itu, berhasil tapi uang ga masuk kan itu masalahnya). Saya balas, sampai sekarang belum ada jawaban lain

Saya awalnay mau followup di live chat, karena pikir saya akan lebih cepat daripada email. Tapi entah kenapa saya tidak bisa buka chat baru, tidak ada tombol/pilihannya. Endingnya stop di "Chat berakhir pada ...." dan gabisa start lagi

Haduh, sejujurnya cape banget. Uang saya hilang, sudah terpotong tapi tidak diterima. Mungkin harus ikhlas saja....

edit: masalah sudah ditangani dan customer care bagian complaint juga sudah telfon ke saya menjelaskan dengan baik kronologinya. terima kasih dan semoga bisa selalu menjadi lebih baik ke depannya

message:
Sudah sempat dipertimbangkan untuk dijadikan bank utama untuk menabung karena bunga deposito sangat bagus dan sudah mendukung QRIS. Berubah pikiran karena pukul 5 pagi ini, transfer ke bank lain tidak bisa dilakukan. Selalu timeout walaupun aplikasi terupdate.

CS live chat yang dihubungi tidak cukup komunikatif dan respon sangat lambat kalau dibandingkan dengan CS bank lain. Tidak ada CS yang menjawab telepon saya. Komentar Instagram yang dinonaktifkan juga membuat saya cemas. 

Sementara dana saya pindahkan dulu (bisa lewat OVO lalu transfer ke bank lain) sampai Superbank bisa menjanjikan CS yang lebih responsif dan helpful. Kejadian ini cukup membuang waktu karena transfer adalah fitur utama yang saya pakai tanpa kenal waktu.

Jika memang ada waktu server off, mohon lebih informatif di semua channel yang dapat diakses pengguna. Terima kasih.
label: Yes
